{"tid":2359792,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"永恆的七十個七次 - 陳也","createTime":"2021-01-09T07:40:03.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-09T07:40:03.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"68705e6ea786aafcb95e402525a1b443cb095c35","tid":2359792,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T07:40:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20210107/MDUPNYF2QNATLAEDREQVBIGFTQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20210107%2FMDUPNYF2QNATLAEDREQVBIGFTQ%2F&d=M%2BQ4vsyFJ%2Bls%2BsYkNkBEXb9ZTfDhdyQuSOQsORMTmv0%3D&h=bba59c2c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20210107%2FMDUPNYF2QNATLAEDREQVBIGFTQ%2F&h=4499a963\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20210107/MDUPNYF2QNATLAEDREQVBIGFTQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n永恆的七十個七次 - 陳也<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/xL_5-ZeIHJoZjGfa2PgQN31bu_0=/1235x718/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/5JUV6KQCQZDBHDP2GPSLFLUG5Y.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FxL_5-ZeIHJoZjGfa2PgQN31bu_0%3D%2F1235x718%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F5JUV6KQCQZDBHDP2GPSLFLUG5Y.png&h=1db8761d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nBNO 5+1大軍未動，深圳灣人潮做了撤離的示範。萬七咁多人打蛇餅，為求逃離疫境，進入大茶飯的清零天堂，排N粒鐘唔打尖都肯制。除了風球落下後趕返工的「HK第一」有得揮，這條「避疫線」，應該穩坐第二。萬七人對林鄭的同心抗疫心領，雙腳最誠實，好L鍾意香港嗎？土生土長鍾意香港的人都被迫流亡，擠在口岸這些來港N年仍然鄉音不改、搵夠就跳船的新香港同胞，示範了風雨同舟的相反模式，近年豪擲公帑美化施政的政府宣傳片，零效果。（九成人唔信！）<br />\n<br />\n同樣大灑公帑但只得41萬人下載的安心出行，蛇齋餅粽投區議會保皇一票那130萬既得利益者，詐瞓！勞動國家隊馳援做全民檢測的170萬人次，打個八折都136萬，與保皇的建制票相若。六位數的逃兵陷局長於極羞恥的不義，講到口臭，萬七人還是老老嫩嫩拉喼走佬向藍牙監控說不。這隻安心碼，注定與底褲口罩，鹿馬共同體。<br />\n<br />\n自稱是天主教徒的薛永恆，。。。。。。。。。"}]}